PATTERN_EXTENSION_FROM_WORKSPACE

static final String PATTERN_EXTENSION_FROM_WORKSPACE
Pattern extension read from the workspace or from the target platform.
Key for a boolean value.
True means that the extension has been loaded from the workspace, false from the target platform.
